      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Mr. Henderson might sigh deeply and say, \"This whole business is getting too complicated; we can't have outsiders coming in trying to upset the fundamental structure here.\" Another might chime in, \"They don't understand how things run in a town like this; they just want to drag us into some chaos.\" A third could agree, \"We've kept this place running smoothly because we maintain our own standards, and sudden disruptions just spoil the good order.\"",
